ihe-sdc-ecc-DiagnosticReport.name: DiagnosticReportSDCeCC
ihe-sdc-ecc-DiagnosticReport.description: A DiagnosticReport Profile meant to capture what should be represented in a report parsed from an IHE SDC Form

ihe-sdc-ecc-DocumentReference.name: DocumentReferenceSDCeCC
ihe-sdc-ecc-DocumentReference.description: A DocumentReference Profile meant to share an IHE SDC Form whether completed or blank

ihe-sdc-ecc-Observation.name: ObservationSDCeCC
ihe-sdc-ecc-Observation.description: A Observation Profile meant to capture Question and Answer Sets from an IHE SDC Form. Questions shold be added as a code and the answer should be added as an appropriate data type. If the answer is a single select it should be added as a valueCodeableConcept. If a Question is a Multiselect then component may be used to list multiple answers
